Duberley-J-D.  King-H.

Cystic fibrosis: the nurse-teacher and carer for mother and child.

CYSTIC-FIBROSIS: nu.  PARENT-CHILD-RELATIONS.  PATIENTS: ed.
PATIENT-EDUCATION.

CHILD.  HOME-NURSING.  HUMAN.  INTERPERSONAL-RELATIONS.
NURSE-PATIENT-RELATIONS.  TERMINAL-CARE.

The authors explain the importance of nursing care being directed to
all members of the family involved in the care of the cystic fibrosis
child and, in particular, the mother.

